<section class="unique-section" id="comparison">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">Why Flowfile</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">What makes it unique</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        Flowfile isn't trying to replace your existing tools. It fills a gap for those who want visual data transformation without lock-in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="unique-grid">
      <div class="unique-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" />
            <path d="M3 9h18" />
            <path d="M9 21V9" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Visual meets code</h3>
        <p>Build pipelines visually, then export as clean Python code. Switch between both anytime â€” no vendor lock-in.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="unique-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" />
            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" />
            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Flexible deployment</h3>
        <p>Run locally with pip, deploy via Docker, or use the desktop app. Your data, your infrastructure, your choice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="unique-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <path d="M12 6v6l4 2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>See your data</h3>
        <p>Preview results at every step of your pipeline. No more running the entire flow just to check one transformation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="unique-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Built on Polars</h3>
        <p>Under the hood, Flowfile uses Polars for fast, memory-efficient data processing. Same performance you'd get in code.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .unique-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .unique-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .unique-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .unique-card .card-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .unique-card .card-icon svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    stroke: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .unique-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .unique-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .unique-section {
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .unique-grid {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .unique-card {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .unique-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 350px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
